## server_build:

git clone https://github.com/pvkraja227/Commerce-website.git

cd Commerce-website/project-files/

sudo docker login (provide details)

sudo chown ubuntu build.sh
sudo chmod 744 build.sh

./build.sh

(check DockerHub)

## server_deploy:

git clone https://github.com/pvkraja227/Commerce-website.git

cd Commerce-website/project-files/

sudo chown ubuntu deploy.sh
sudo chmod 744 deploy.sh

./deploy.sh

kubectl get pods -n react-nginx (previous pods got deleted and new pods started)
